- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper discusses controller synthesis for continuous systems. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the paper deals with symbolic abstractions and their composition, which are relevant to programming language semantics. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is another possible category as the paper discusses networks of interacting components. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with automated controller synthesis.
